DAY
1
(-/L/D)
Pick up at airport (or hotel), Transfer to Grand World Phuquoc (The Sleepless City), Photo stop at Dinh Cau Temple, Free at Grand World Phuquoc, Grand World Nightly Light Show, Dinner, ON Phuquoc
Optional Activities at Grand World Phu Quoc:

Phu Quoc Teddy Bear Museum Admission: $8 USD/pax
Venice River Boat Gondola: $8 USD/pax
The Quintessence of Vietnam" Show Ticket: $12 USD/pax
DAY
2
(B/L/D)
Breafast, Fullday visit Hon Thom Island, Aquatopia Water Park, (include cable car, buffet), Sun Set Town, Kiss Bridge, Dinner ON Phuquoc
Optional Shows at Sunset Town:
For a cultural experience, you can pay an additional $12 USD per person to watch the Symphony of the Sea Show (7:45 PM – 8:10 PM).
For the grand finale, upgrade to see the Kiss of the Sea main show, which includes spectacular fireworks (9:00 PM – 9:30 PM). The price is $45 USD for two people or $35 USD for one person. (Note: This show is not performed on Tuesdays).
DAY
3
(B)
Breakfast, Ho Quoc Temple, Shopping, End of tour
